node.text:
While tourists from the northern hemisphere sunbathe on the beaches,
we think it made sense to introduce you to our South Island and Cloudy Bay shores.

From our beaches to yours, good sunbathing to all. ☀️
Lay down and extend the experience on our igtv.

Sound on 🔊

Please drink responsibly. 

#cloudybay #fromourworldtoyours #nzwine #newzealand #marlborough #slowtv

node.text:
Psssst. Yes you. Shut your email, give those bleary eyes a rest and come settle down for a nap under the trees by our Marlborough vineyard. 🌳🍇🌳

A little rest and relaxation.

#fromourworldtoyours #timetofeel #cloudybay #newzealand #nzwine #vineyard #marlborough #slowtv

node.title: Cloudy Bay Slow TV under the trees

node.text:
What vantage point offers the best views of our Marlborough vineyards? 🍇

Hint: ⬆️ Take off with us for a flight of fancy.

Sound on 🔊

#Fromourworldtoyours #CloudyBay #NewZealand

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Cloudy Bay on August 31, 2021 tagging @alivelikethewind. May be an image of 1 person, outdoors and text that says 'BAY CLOUDY'.

node.text:
We know that haven can mean different things to different people. Whether you're forever chasing sunsets like @alivelikethewind, here's a tip for those still searching for their haven: sometimes the best sanctuary is the one that's right in front of us.

Please drink responsibly.

#CloudyBay #FromOurHavenToYours #HavenChaser

node.text:
We’re about to slip into the cool crispness of spring. What’s your favourite season, and why?

Please drink responsibly.

#NaturesFinest #NaturesWonder #PureNewZealand #FromOurHavenToYours

node.text:
It might be mid-winter here in New Zealand, but the work never stops in our vineyards. Tell us: what’s your favourite wind-down ritual after a long day?

Please drink responsibly.

#CloudyBay #FromOurHaventoYours #MeanwhileInNZ #NZWine

node.text:

Please drink responsibly.

#CloudyBay #SunshineAndWine
